I rebased my changes on top of master, fixing the resulting merge conflicts and applying @girving's comments.
In order to get the tests to pass, I've converted a few more of the ops to complex128, but I tried to keep it minimal in order to not conflict with @hunkim's PR too much.

Also, I didn't commit the ops.pbtxt, as it seems that there are currently some unrelated ops on master for which the ops.pbtxt hasn't been committed yet.

body:
I rebased my changes on top of `master`, fixing the resulting merge conflicts and applying @girving's comments.
In order to get the tests to pass, I've converted a few more of the ops to `complex128`, but I tried to keep it minimal in order to not conflict with @hunkim's PR too much.

Also, I didn't commit the `ops.pbtxt`, as it seems that there are currently some unrelated ops on `master` for which the `ops.pbtxt` hasn't been committed yet.
